This directory contains data vendored from the SALLM project:

  SALLM: Security Assessment of LLM Generated Code
  https://github.com/s2e-lab/SALLM  (commit 0159a63)
  Copyright the SALLM authors.
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (see LICENSE).

Only the prompt dataset (Dataset/dataset.jsonl — 100 security-focused Python
prompts, each with an inline insecure reference solution) is retained and used
by this project, as the source of evaluation prompts.

SALLM's own evaluation/generation harness is NOT used here: in this project the
security verification of generated code is performed by static analysis with
CodeQL (the codeql-eval skill), not by SALLM's dynamic test harness.

Changes from upstream (as required by the Apache License, Section 4): only
Dataset/dataset.jsonl and this LICENSE/NOTICE are kept; all other files
(.git, .gitignore, README.md, Evaluation/, Generation/, util-scripts/, and the
remaining Dataset/ entries: Assertion/, Matching/, Tainted/, multi-dataset.jsonl,
Dataset_creator.ipynb) were removed.
